EFFECT ON THE SAVED STATES OF PLAY.YOU CAN CHOOSE WETHER YOU WANT TO LOAD TEAM
1 OR TEAM 2.TEAM 1 IS USUALLY YOUR TEAM AND TEAM 2 IS THE COMPUTERS TEAM. THIS
MAKES IT POSSIBLE FOR 2 PLAYERS TO HAVE THEIR MANAGER TEAMS PLAY AGAINST EACH
OTHER. AFTER CLICKING ON TO ONE OF THE 2 FIELDS THERE APPEARS A FILE SELECTION
BOX. IF YOU ARE PLAYING FROM THE HARD DISK YOU WILL NOW SEE A DISPLAY OF ALL
SAVED STATES OF PLAY LISTED(A MAXIMUM OF 5 TEAMS) IF YOU ARE PLAYING FROM A
FLOPPY DISK YOU MUST NOW INSERT THE DISK CONTAINING YOUR SAVED STATES OF PLAY
AND THEN CLICK ONTO THE`DRIVE` FIELD. THEN TYPE A:OR B:(DEPENDING ON THE DRIVE
IN USE)FOLLOWED BY RETURN/ENTER.AFTER A SHORT DELAY,THE LIS OF SAVED STATES OF
PLAY APPEARS. CLICK ONTO THAT STATE OF PLAY FROM WHICH YOU WISH TO DRAW THE
TEAM FOR THIS ACTION GAME.
