SECTION,PLEASE READ THESE LINES WITH SPECIAL ATTENTION OTHERWISE YOU MAY FIND
YOURSELF CURSING YOUR JOYSTICK OR MOUSE.
CONTROL OF THE PLAYERS,THERE ARE 2 TEAMS ON THE PLAYING FIELD. THE TEAM IN
LIGHT BLUE PLAYS FROM BOTTOM TO TOP(THIS MEANS THAT IT IS TRYING TO THROW A
FLONK INTO THE UPPER POTT) TEAM 2 IS IN DARK BLUE AND PLAYS FROM TOP TO
BOTTOM.AS A RULE YOU CONTROL TEAM 1 AND THE COMPUTER CONTROLS TEAM 2. SOME
PLAYERS ARE SPECIALLY MARKED.

PLAYER IN BALL POSSESSION    ;-  2 SMALL YELLOW TRIANGLES (TEAM 1)
                                 2 SMALL RED TRIANGLES (TEAM 2)

PLAYER WARNED BY REF         ;-  1 YELLOW TRIANGLE(TEAM 1)
                                 1 RED TRIANGLE (TEAM 2)

PLAYER CONTROLLED BY PLAYER 1;-  WHITE ARROW
(TEAM IRRELEVANT)

PLAYER CONTROLLED BY PLAYER 2;-  BLACK ARROW
(TEAM IRRELEVANT)

